  "text": "Once uploaded, the users can browse and query the 3D genome as described above. In addition to the reference data stored in our database, the users can now access simultaneously the reference SNPs collected from (24) together with those stored in the local file. To prevent any privacy issues, user data are stored locally and not transmitted to our e103 Nucleic Acids Research, 2015, Vol. 43, No. 16 PAGE 6 OF 9 server. A similar solution has been adopted by the UCSC genome browser [CITATION_1] .",
